Articles.Content: Sorry i forgot to tell you guys but im on vacation in Houston Tx today we saw the NASA Houston Space center got a All access to the NBL (neutral Buoyancy lab) where we actually saw astronaughts practice underwater up close Physically got to stand next to them before they dived and got to see a MODEL scale Saturn V i took picture\'s i will upload them when i get back in like 1-2 days the engines on the first stage are like MOUNTAINS. Anyways so far its been great. 8)
Gee, thanks for telling us. We\'ll sure miss you.
